    "text": [
        "Dear Mr Rupert,",
        "I am writing to inform you of the unavailability of hot water due to a mechanical fault in the solar water heater panel. The situation has become intolerable.",
        "Let me explain my situation in more detail. As you know, we are transitioning into the early winter period and without hot water, maintaining personal hygiene is challenging or rather very uncomfortable; Especially in the morning hours, the water is too cold to touch. Therefore, I am not able to take care of my basic needs.",
        "Would you kindly consider the solution I suggest? If I could get an electric water heater, until the solar panel gets fixed, then I could manage my circumstances well. I believe this is a cheap and quick action we can implement. I request you to take this matter with utmost priority and resolve it.",
        "I look forward to hearing from you.",
        "Yours Sincerely,",
        "Krish"
    ],
